Subject: [PATCH 1198/1594] MLK-10256-08: dts: Add mipi csi support to imx7
 19x19 arm2

commit 53a0d291c22119dcbcb09281ed3bb2048461f581 from
git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git

Add new imx7d-19x19-ddr3-arm2-mipi.dts file for mipi csi.
Move parallel csi config to imx7d-19x19-ddr3-arm2-csi.dts.

Signed-off-by: Sandor Yu <R01008@freescale.com>
